Day 15 â€“ Light Logic Building (int array, loops, variables only)                                                                                
  
Q1: Ek array hai {2, 4, 6}. Har element ko 3 se add karke print karo.
Hint: System.out.println(arr[i] + 3);

Q2: Ek array {10, 20, 30, 40} ke pehle 2 elements ka difference print karo.
Hint: arr[1] - arr[0]

Q3: Ek array {5, 10, 15} ke elements ka sum nikalo bina loop ke.
Hint: Direct add karo: arr[0] + arr[1] + arr[2]

Q4: Array {1, 2, 3, 4} me kitne elements hai? Length print karo.
Hint: arr.length

Q5: Ek array hai {8, 6, 4}. Sabhi elements ka total sum print karo.
Hint: loop + sum variable

Q6: Array {9, 3, 7} ka sabse bada number print karo.
Hint: max variable + loop

Q7: Array {5, 10, 15, 20} me sirf even numbers print karo.
Hint: if (arr[i] % 2 == 0)

Q8: Array {1, 3, 5, 7, 9} ke har element me +1 karke print karo.

Q9: Array {100, 200, 300} ko reverse order me print karo.
Hint: i = arr.length - 1 se loop start karo

Q10: Array {2, 4, 6, 8} ka average print karo.
Hint: sum nikalo â†’ sum / arr.length

