IUC 1: Ek array banao with 4 values aur uska sabse chhota number print karo.
Hint: min variable + loop

IUC 2: Array {1, 2, 3, 4, 5} me sirf odd numbers print karo.
Hint: if (arr[i] % 2 != 0)

IUC 3: Array {10, 20, 30, 40} ke pehle do elements ka sum print karo.

IUC 4: Array {2, 3, 4} me har value ko 2 se multiply karke print karo.

IUC 5: Array {3, 6, 9} ke har element ka square print karo.
Hint: arr[i] * arr[i]
